<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Billel ZIGHAB — Architecte Solution Senior</title>
<meta name="description" content="Billel ZIGHAB — Architecte Solution & Entreprise Senior · 17+ ans d'expérience · TOGAF, Cloud, Microservices, Sécurité.">
<meta property="og:type" content="profile">
<meta property="og:title" content="Billel ZIGHAB — Architecte Solution Senior">
<meta property="og:description" content="17+ ans en architecture IT · TOGAF, Cloud (Azure/AWS), Microservices, Sécurité · Disponible en freelance.">
<meta property="og:image" content="photo.jpg">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#f6f8fc; --bg2:#eef2fb; --card:#ffffff; --bd:#e6ebf5;
    --ink:#1d2333; --soft:#5b6480; --muted:#8b94ad;
    --brand:#4f6ef7; --brand2:#7c4dff; --brandSoft:#eef1ff; --accent:#10b981;
    --halo1:#dbe4ff; --halo2:#ede4ff;
    --disp:"Plus Jakarta Sans",system-ui,sans-serif; --sans:"Inter",system-ui,sans-serif; --maxw:1120px;
    --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(40,60,120,.08); --shadow2:0 18px 50px rgba(40,60,120,.12);
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--sans);line-height:1.65;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden}
  a{color:var(--brand);text-decoration:none}
  h1,h2,h3,.disp{font-family:var(--disp)}
  .wrap{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:0 26px}
  ::selection{background:var(--brandSoft)}

  /* nav */
  .topbar{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:60;backdrop-filter:blur(10px);background:rgba(246,248,252,.82);border-bottom:1px solid var(--bd)}
  .topbar .wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:66px}
  .logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px}
  .logo .mark{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:11px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:800;color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .logo .nm{font-weight:700;font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.1}
  .logo .nm small{display:none;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;font-size:.68rem}
  html[lang="fr"] .logo .nm small[data-lang="fr"],html[lang="en"] .logo .nm small[data-lang="en"]{display:block}
  .nav{display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center}
  .nav a.lk{color:var(--soft);font-size:.92rem;font-weight:600;padding:6px 4px;position:relative;transition:color .25s}
  .nav a.lk::after{content:"";position:absolute;left:0;right:0;bottom:-3px;height:2.5px;border-radius:3px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));transform:scaleX(0);transform-origin:center;transition:transform .3s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1)}
  .nav a.lk:hover{color:var(--brand)}
  .nav a.lk:hover::after{transform:scaleX(.6)}
  .nav a.lk.active{color:var(--brand)}
  .nav a.lk.active::after{transform:scaleX(1)}
  /* reading progress bar */
  #progress{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:3px;width:0;z-index:80;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));transition:width .1s linear}
  #bgwrap{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden}
  #bgimg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:
    radial-gradient(1000px 900px at 100% 50%,rgba(124,92,255,.20),transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(1000px 900px at 0% 50%,rgba(79,110,247,.14),transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(90deg,#f0eefc 0%,#f7f6fe 50%,#f0ecfb 100%)}
  .hero,.ribbon,section,footer{position:relative;z-index:1}
  #skills,#edu{background:transparent!important}
  section{scroll-margin-top:80px}
  .langtog{display:inline-flex;background:var(--brandSoft);border-radius:999px;padding:3px}
  .langtog button{background:transparent;color:var(--soft);border:0;padding:6px 13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;font-size:.78rem;border-radius:999px}
  .langtog button.active{background:#fff;color:var(--brand);box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  @media(max-width:820px){.nav a.lk{display:none}}

  /* HERO */
  .hero{position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:
    radial-gradient(680px 460px at 82% 18%,var(--halo2),transparent 62%),
    radial-gradient(720px 520px at 8% 0%,var(--halo1),transparent 60%),
    linear-gradient(180deg,#fff,transparent 40%);z-index:0}
  .hero .wrap{position:relative;z-index:1;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:46px;align-items:center;padding:58px 26px 64px;min-height:60vh}
  @media(max-width:880px){.hero .wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;padding-top:36px}.photo-col{order:-1}}
  .badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    padding:7px 14px;border-radius:999px;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--soft);margin-bottom:20px}
  .badge .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(16,185,129,.18)}
  .hello{font-size:clamp(2.4rem,6vw,4rem);line-height:1.06;margin:0;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-1.2px}
  .hello .wave{display:inline-block;animation:wave 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;transform-origin:70% 70%}
  @keyframes wave{0%,60%,100%{transform:rotate(0)}10%{transform:rotate(16deg)}20%{transform:rotate(-8deg)}30%{transform:rotate(14deg)}40%{transform:rotate(-4deg)}}
  .hello .name{background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}
  .subrole{font-size:clamp(.92rem,1.8vw,1.08rem);color:var(--brand);margin:14px 0 0;font-weight:600;line-height:1.45;max-width:560px}
  @media(max-width:880px){.subrole{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}}
  .blurb{color:var(--soft);max-width:520px;margin:14px auto 0;font-size:1.05rem}
  @media(min-width:881px){.blurb{margin-left:0}}
  .social{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-top:24px;justify-content:center}
  @media(min-width:881px){.social{justify-content:flex-start}}
  .social a{width:44px;height:44px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:13px;display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--brand);transition:.22s;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .social a:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);background:var(--brand);color:#fff}
  .social svg{width:18px;height:18px}
  .hero-cta{display:flex;gap:13px;margin-top:26px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
  @media(min-width:881px){.hero-cta{justify-content:flex-start}}
  .btn{padding:13px 24px;border-radius:13px;font-weight:700;font-size:.92rem;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--bd);background:#fff;color:var(--ink);transition:.22s;box-shadow:var(--shadow);font-family:var(--disp)}
  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}
  .btn.primary{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));color:#fff;border:0}
  .dl{position:relative;display:inline-block}
  .dl-menu{position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 8px);left:0;min-width:200px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:14px;box-shadow:var(--shadow2);padding:6px;opacity:0;visibility:hidden;transform:translateY(-6px);transition:.2s;z-index:30}
  .dl-menu.open{opacity:1;visibility:visible;transform:none}
  .dl-menu a{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:9px;color:var(--ink);font-weight:600;font-size:.92rem}
  .dl-menu a:hover{background:var(--brandSoft);color:var(--brand)}
  .dl-menu .dlflag{font-size:1.05rem}

  /* photo */
  .photo-col{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:16px}
  .photo-strip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);box-shadow:var(--shadow);border-radius:999px;padding:9px 18px;font-size:.82rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--soft)}
  .photo-strip b{color:var(--brand);font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:800}
  .photo-strip .sep{width:1px;height:14px;background:var(--bd)}
  .blob{position:relative;width:min(380px,82vw);aspect-ratio:1/1;display:grid;place-items:center}
  .blob .bgblob{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));
    border-radius:42% 58% 56% 44%/52% 44% 56% 48%;animation:morph 9s ease-in-out infinite;box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}
  @keyframes morph{0%,100%{border-radius:42% 58% 56% 44%/52% 44% 56% 48%}50%{border-radius:56% 44% 48% 52%/44% 56% 44% 56%}}
  .blob img{position:relative;z-index:2;width:80%;height:88%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center top;border-radius:28px;border:5px solid #fff;box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}
  .blob .ph{position:relative;z-index:2;width:88%;height:88%;border-radius:32px;display:grid;place-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.16);color:#fff;font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:800;font-size:5rem;backdrop-filter:blur(2px)}
  .chip{position:absolute;z-index:3;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);box-shadow:var(--shadow2);border-radius:14px;padding:9px 13px;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
  .chip small{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;font-size:.66rem}
  .chip.c1{top:8%;left:-6%}.chip.c2{bottom:10%;right:-6%}
  @media(max-width:880px){.chip.c1{left:2%}.chip.c2{right:2%}}

  /* ribbon */
  .ribbon{margin-top:-26px;position:relative;z-index:5}
  .ribbon .wrap{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px}
  @media(max-width:720px){.ribbon .wrap{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
  .rb{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:16px;padding:20px;text-align:center;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .rb .n{font-family:var(--disp);font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--brand)}
  .rb .l{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;margin-top:2px}
  .langtile{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:2px}
  .lflags{display:flex;gap:9px;margin-top:8px}
  .lf{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:4px;cursor:default}
  .lf .fg{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:50%;overflow:hidden;display:block;border:1px solid var(--bd);box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:transform .2s}
  .lf .fg svg,.lf .fg img{width:100%;height:100%;display:block;object-fit:cover}
  .lf:hover .fg{transform:translateY(-3px) scale(1.06)}
  .lf b{font-size:.68rem;letter-spacing:.5px;color:var(--soft);font-weight:700}

  section{padding:60px 0;position:relative}
  .sec-h{text-align:center;margin-bottom:38px}
  .sec-h .k{display:none;color:var(--brand);background:var(--brandSoft);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:999px;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700}
  html[lang="fr"] .sec-h .k[data-lang="fr"],html[lang="en"] .sec-h .k[data-lang="en"],.sec-h .k:not([data-lang]){display:inline-block}
  .sec-h h2{font-size:clamp(1.7rem,3.6vw,2.3rem);margin:14px 0 0;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.5px}
  .lead{color:var(--soft);max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;font-size:1.06rem;text-align:center}
  #about .lead{font-size:1.22rem;color:var(--ink);font-weight:500;line-height:1.5}
  .pillars{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:18px;margin:30px auto 0;max-width:1000px}
  @media(max-width:820px){.pillars{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:480px}}
  .pillar{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:18px;padding:24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:.25s}
  .pillar:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}
  .pillar .pic{width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:13px;display:grid;place-items:center;background:var(--brandSoft);color:var(--brand);margin-bottom:14px}
  .pillar .pic svg{width:24px;height:24px}
  .pillar h3{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:1.04rem;font-weight:800}
  .pillar p{margin:0;color:var(--soft);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.55}
  .ground{max-width:880px;margin:26px auto 0;text-align:center;font-style:italic;color:var(--muted);font-size:.95rem}

  /* skills */
  .skills{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:18px;margin-top:8px}
  @media(max-width:780px){.skills{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .skill{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:18px;padding:22px;transition:.25s;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .skill:hover{transform:translateY(-5px);box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}
  .skill h3{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:1.02rem;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px}
  .skill h3 .i{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:9px;display:grid;place-items:center;background:var(--brandSoft);color:var(--brand);font-size:1rem}
  .tags{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
  .tag{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--soft);background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--bd);padding:5px 11px;border-radius:9px;font-weight:500}
  .skill.feat{grid-column:1/-1;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff,var(--brandSoft));border-color:#d7defe}

  /* timeline */
  .tl{position:relative;max-width:940px;margin:0 auto;padding-left:30px;border-left:2px solid var(--bd)}
  .job{position:relative;margin-bottom:22px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:18px;padding:22px 24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow);transition:.25s}
  .job:hover{box-shadow:var(--shadow2);transform:translateY(-2px)}
  .job::before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-39px;top:26px;width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--brand);border:3px solid #fff;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px var(--brandSoft)}
  .job .top{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:space-between;gap:6px;align-items:baseline}
  .job .co{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:800;font-size:1.12rem;color:var(--ink)}
  .job .co b{color:var(--brand);font-weight:800}
  .job .co .proj{color:var(--soft);font-weight:600}
  .job .date{color:#fff;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));font-size:.74rem;font-weight:700;padding:4px 11px;border-radius:999px;white-space:nowrap}
  .job .ro{color:var(--soft);font-weight:600;font-size:.94rem;margin:4px 0 6px}
  .job .tag{font-style:italic;color:var(--brand);font-size:.92rem;margin:0 0 10px;padding-left:11px;border-left:3px solid var(--brand);font-weight:500}
  .job ul{margin:8px 0 0;padding-left:18px}
  .job li{margin:6px 0;color:#3b4considered;color:#3a4considered}
  .job li{color:#3b4366;font-size:.93rem}
  .job li::marker{color:var(--brand)}
  .job .meta{margin-top:12px;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);background:var(--bg2);border-radius:12px;padding:11px 14px}
  .job .meta b{color:var(--soft)}
  .more-btn{display:block;margin:8px auto 0;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--bd);color:var(--brand);padding:12px 26px;border-radius:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:var(--shadow);font-family:var(--disp)}
  .more-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}

  .two{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;max-width:940px;margin:0 auto}
  @media(max-width:760px){.two{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .card2{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--bd);border-radius:18px;padding:24px;box-shadow:var(--shadow)}
  .card2 h3{margin:0 0 10px;font-size:1.12rem;font-weight:800}
  .card2 p,.card2 li{color:var(--soft);font-size:.93rem}
  .card2 ul{padding-left:18px;margin:0}
  .card2 li{margin:8px 0}
  .card2 li::marker{color:var(--brand)}

  .contact-box{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--brand),var(--brand2));border-radius:24px;padding:44px 30px;color:#fff;box-shadow:var(--shadow2)}
  .contact-box h2{color:#fff;font-size:1.8rem;margin:0 0 8px}
  .contact-box p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);margin:0 0 22px}
  .contact-box .btn{background:#fff;color:var(--brand);border:0}
  .contact-box .btn.ghost{background:rgba(255,255,255,.14);color:#fff}

  footer{padding:40px 0;text-align:center;color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem;border-top:1px solid var(--bd)}
  footer .nm{font-family:var(--disp);font-weight:800;color:var(--ink);font-size:1.1rem}

  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease}
  .reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
  [data-lang]{display:none}
  html[lang="fr"] [data-lang="fr"],html[lang="en"] [data-lang="en"]{display:revert}
  @media print{.topbar,.hero-cta,.langtog,.more-btn,.social{display:none}body{background:#fff}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="progress"></div>
<div id="bgwrap" aria-hidden="true"><div id="bgimg"></div></div>
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="mark">BZ</div>
      <div class="nm">Billel ZIGHAB<small data-lang="fr">Senior Solution Architect</small><small data-lang="en">Senior Solution Architect</small></div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav">
      <a class="lk" href="#about" data-lang="fr">Profil</a><a class="lk" href="#about" data-lang="en">About</a>
      <a class="lk" href="#skills" data-lang="fr">Compétences</a><a class="lk" href="#skills" data-lang="en">Skills</a>
      <a class="lk" href="#exp" data-lang="fr">Expérience</a><a class="lk" href="#exp" data-lang="en">Experience</a>
      <a class="lk" href="#contact">Contact</a>
      <span class="langtog">
        <button id="bfr" class="active" onclick="setLang('fr')">FR</button>
        <button id="ben" onclick="setLang('en')">EN</button>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="intro-col">
      <span class="badge"><span class="dot"></span><span data-lang="fr">Disponible pour missions freelance</span><span data-lang="en">Available for freelance</span></span>
      <h1 class="hello" data-lang="fr">Bonjour <span class="wave">👋</span><br>je suis <span class="name"> Billel</span></h1>
      <h1 class="hello" data-lang="en">Hello <span class="wave">👋</span><br>I'm <span class="name">Billel</span></h1>
      <p class="subrole" data-lang="fr">Senior Solution Architect | Cloud &amp; Enterprise Architecture | Azure · AWS · AI/ML Integration | Zero Trust | TOGAF | London, Paris</p>
      <p class="subrole" data-lang="en">Senior Solution Architect | Cloud &amp; Enterprise Architecture | Azure · AWS · AI/ML Integration | Zero Trust | TOGAF | London, Paris</p>
      <p class="blurb" data-lang="fr">Je transforme le besoin métier en architectures cibles robustes, sécurisées et évolutives — du cadrage jusqu'à la gouvernance. 17+ ans d'expérience IT.</p>
      <p class="blurb" data-lang="en">I turn business needs into robust, secure and scalable target architectures — from framing to governance. 17+ years in IT.</p>
      <div class="social">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/billel-zighab-510b3952/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="LinkedIn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4.98 3.5a2.5 2.5 0 11-.02 5 2.5 2.5 0 01.02-5zM3 9h4v12H3zM9 9h3.8v1.7h.05c.53-1 1.83-2.05 3.77-2.05 4.03 0 4.78 2.65 4.78 6.1V21H21v-5.4c0-1.3-.02-2.96-1.8-2.96-1.8 0-2.08 1.4-2.08 2.86V21H9z"/></svg></a>
        <a href="mailto:billel.zighab@gmail.com" aria-label="Email"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="5" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M3 7l9 6 9-6"/></svg></a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a class="btn primary" href="CV_Billel-ZIGHAB_FR_SolutionArchitect.pdf" download data-lang="fr">⤓ Télécharger le CV</a>
        <a class="btn primary" href="CV_Billel-ZIGHAB_EN_SolutionArchitect.pdf" download data-lang="en">⤓ Download CV</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#contact" data-lang="fr">Me contacter</a>
        <a class="btn" href="#contact" data-lang="en">Get in touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="photo-col">
      <div class="blob">
        <div class="bgblob"></div>
        <img src="photo.jpg" alt="Billel ZIGHAB" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='grid';">
        <div class="ph" style="display:none">MP</div>
      </div>
      <div class="photo-strip">
        <span><b>10+</b> <span data-lang="fr">ans d'architecture</span><span data-lang="en">yrs in architecture</span></span>
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>TOGAF</span>
        <span class="sep"></span>
        <span>Azure · AWS</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="ribbon">
  <div class="wrap">
