<section id="about">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-h reveal"><span class="k" data-lang="fr">Profil</span><span class="k" data-lang="en">Profile</span><h2 data-lang="fr">Résumé professionnel</h2><h2 data-lang="en">Professional summary</h2></div>
    <p class="lead reveal" data-lang="fr" style="text-align:center;max-width:820px">J'aide les organisations à transformer une vision métier en plateformes critiques claires, sécurisées et durables — du premier échange jusqu'à la production.</p>
    <p class="lead reveal" data-lang="en" style="text-align:center;max-width:820px">I help organisations turn business vision into critical platforms that are clear, secure and built to last — from the first conversation to production.</p>

    <div class="pillars">
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <span class="pic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="3.5" width="14" height="17" rx="2.5"/><path d="M9 3.5h6v2.2H9zM8.4 11l1.6 1.6 3-3.4M8.4 16.2l1.6 1.6 3-3.4"/></svg></span>
        <h3 data-lang="fr">Gouvernance &amp; standards (TOGAF)</h3><h3 data-lang="en">Governance &amp; standards (TOGAF)</h3>
        <p data-lang="fr">Pilotage d'instances (Design Authority, comités d'architecture) et livrables décisionnels : DAT, HLD/LLD, ADR, cartographie applicative.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Driving governance bodies (Design Authority, architecture committees) and decision-ready deliverables: DAT, HLD/LLD, ADR, application landscape maps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <span class="pic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="5" cy="12" r="2.4"/><circle cx="19" cy="5.5" r="2.4"/><circle cx="19" cy="18.5" r="2.4"/><path d="M7.1 11l9.8-4.5M7.1 13l9.8 4.5"/></svg></span>
        <h3 data-lang="fr">Architecture &amp; intégration</h3><h3 data-lang="en">Architecture &amp; integration</h3>
        <p data-lang="fr">Conception de bout en bout d'écosystèmes distribués modernes (Microservices, Event-Driven &amp; Real-Time, API-first) et intégration de capacités IA/ML au sein du SI d'entreprise.</p>
        <p data-lang="en">End-to-end design of modern distributed ecosystems (Microservices, Event-Driven &amp; Real-Time, API-first) and integration of AI/ML capabilities into the enterprise IS.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar reveal">
        <span class="pic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l7 2.5v5c0 4.3-2.9 7.7-7 8.9-4.1-1.2-7-4.6-7-8.9v-5z"/><path d="M12 10.5v3.2M12 10.5a1.4 1.4 0 110-2.8 1.4 1.4 0 010 2.8z"/></svg></span>
        <h3 data-lang="fr">Sécurité &amp; résilience</h3><h3 data-lang="en">Security &amp; resilience</h3>
        <p data-lang="fr">Sécurité by design (Zero Trust, RGPD), exigences non-fonctionnelles (haute disponibilité, PRA/PCA) et optimisation des coûts cloud (Azure / AWS).</p>
        <p data-lang="en">Security by design (Zero Trust, GDPR), non-functional requirements (high availability, DRP/BCP) and cloud cost optimisation (Azure / AWS).</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="ground reveal" data-lang="fr">Issu du terrain — développeur, référent technique puis architecte applicatif — je connais les systèmes de l'intérieur, ce qui me donne la légitimité nécessaire pour choisir les bons composants et garantir la faisabilité réelle des solutions.</p>
    <p class="ground reveal" data-lang="en">From the ground up — developer, technical lead, then application architect — I know systems from the inside, which earns me the right to pick the right components and guarantee solutions that are genuinely feasible.</p>
  </div>
</section>

